lead_paragraph: Katie Ledecky's schedule in Rio is all set. The teenager will go for gold in three individual events after closing her U.S. swimming trials with another dominating performance.

headline.print_headline: Katie Ledecky Set to Swim 3 Freestyle Events in Rio
